<headline>Special Weather Statement issued June 25 at 12:23PM MDT  by NWS GreatFalls</headline>
<description>...Scattered Thunderstorm Capable of Gusty Erratic Winds...
Scattered showers an thunderstorms are developing in terrain
across the region this afternoon. The primary concern will be for
gusty erratic winds in excess of 40 mph, with lightning, briefly
heavy rain, and small hail being a secondary concern.
Thunderstorms will gradually move onto adjacent lower elevation
areas through the afternoon.</description>
